m until he shows that he follows the command of the Book and the Sunnah.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37417,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/23\/taqseer-salah-journey\/","url_meta":{"origin":13629,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Sunnah to shorten prayer during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Muwarriq al-\u2018Ijli reported: He asked Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about prayer during travel. Ibn Umar said, \u201cTwo cycles, two cycles. Whoever opposes the Sunnah has disbelieved.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf 'Abd al-Razza\u0304q 4281 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0651\u0642\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u062c\u0652\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u0636\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25299,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/shafii-leave-opinion-for-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":13629,"position":5},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Sunnah: Leave my opinion if it contradicts Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawawi reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf a prophetic narration is authenticated and it contradicts my opinion, act according to the narration and abandon my opinion.\u201d Source: al-Majmu\u0304\u2019 Sharh\u0323 al-Muhadhab 1\/104 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0648\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0625\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0635\u064e\u062d\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062b\u064f \u062e\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u0650\u064a \u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062b\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064f\u0648\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13629","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13629"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13629\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\